      • onSyncDataResult

        void onSyncDataResult(java.util.List<SyncRawData> datas)
        All sync raw data.This is the only method that is not called by the main thread. Because the data may be very much. In the synchronization process, this method may be called 0 or more times. The data type in the list is the same for one call.
        Parameters:
        datas - Sync raw datas.List is not empty, and size > 0.
